{"tid":34480,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有讀DSE中國文學既你快啲入黎取暖","createTime":"2016-12-11T13:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-03T14:58:15.000Z","uid":45218,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22eed11c6cac0d7655257bc63594288dd7bb6c8d","tid":34480,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"大家都知 呢科真係好少人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> marking scheme 又得果幾粒字 好虛無縹緲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇啲上左岸、過往公開試文學考得好好既巴絲黎分享下你讀呢科既心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼見學校好多平時讀文學幾叻既師兄師姐 好多都失晒手 得lv3、4 ，呢科少人讀到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出去買pp都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以速速開返個post比我地有心讀文學既取下暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 2017DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望5月4大家一齊拎好成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375fa87a8b77b66e9d2b6407ccea31f7e670c758","tid":34480,"uid":4613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"背曬書未？<br />\n<br />\n利申 11AL F---&gt;12AL A"},{"pid":"d9ba5f5491017dcf5edfd76af31fc901b742187a","tid":34480,"uid":36107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:28:48.000Z","msg":"諗住考完哂要考既科再溫<br />\n咁早溫一定唔會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96939b3d2e0b1c19e76a7cc95f27075aa313d9d3","tid":34480,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背曬書未？<br />\n<br />\n利申 11AL F---&amp;gt;12AL A</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大致上都背得七七八八 但有啲長既課文 例如紅樓夢 果啲仲唔係太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打可唔可以分享下溫書 考試心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf42ab1da056321c2a955a6ec877b874a9b048f","tid":34480,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"上年溫左一星期<br />\n最後level 3"},{"pid":"7743bd2ef0f95268d1ac8f44cda0bba85c82f6fe","tid":34480,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住考完哂要考既科再溫<br />\n咁早溫一定唔會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得一篇文至少要溫三次先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以而家溫定差唔多 臨考之前再溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26aebe34e66cd2f34f9649296c275fdf3ec1488","tid":34480,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年溫左一星期<br />\n最後level 3</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都識得有個平時幾叻既師姐 上年3左文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628a1d6c7ece75fb6fdf011e147c3f0c85d2e862","tid":34480,"uid":45897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"係學校成績唔算太差出到去攞3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成績最top既都得4<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8796b30abce6be509fc88c9feee161fbc0ff3d07","tid":34480,"uid":4613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>背曬書未？<br />\n<br />\n利申 11AL F---&gt;12AL A</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大致上都背得七七八八 但有啲長既課文 例如紅樓夢 果啲仲唔係太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打可唔可以分享下溫書 考試心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一字記之曰，抄。<br />\n抄曬所有課文，你無睇錯，係抄曬<br />\n最起碼有底先，之後再慢慢講"},{"pid":"a86b5dbb07f85ec6c2e89228f168ac49c7d60085","tid":34480,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年溫左一星期<br />\n最後level 3</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都識得有個平時幾叻既師姐 上年3左文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前年先岩 即係15年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb62a70df1467f76351975856136bb8df78a715","tid":34480,"uid":32324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"祝好運<br />\n<br />\n利申：15 5星"},{"pid":"071ac7be1db1bcb0d8d977ec6869e8c1194aaee0","tid":34480,"uid":36107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗住考完哂要考既科再溫<br />\n咁早溫一定唔會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得一篇文至少要溫三次先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以而家溫定差唔多 臨考之前再溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我溫10次都冇用 我而加連蒹葭都背唔出<br />\n諗住靠short term memory考"},{"pid":"e6cab2b576f5471b09fae83199a6115b1963f442","tid":34480,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係學校成績唔算太差出到去攞3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成績最top既都得4<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩年前校內考mock 賞析51/60 出到去4撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9831514854e8185fa968127d06b1d849ac5d9c5d","tid":34480,"uid":48368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"易合格難高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d57a9d75b744ce6a2a773edf27a836da22d14d","tid":34480,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"文學要睇翻歷屆幾年 再揀課文黎搵啦<br />\n寫notes背熟引文係基本<br />\n作文都好好好重要<br />\n利申15年 lv5"},{"pid":"ae3a521f874f506ef61009dc5a8cf92f47a12074","tid":34480,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文學要睇翻歷屆幾年 再揀課文黎搵啦<br />\n寫notes背熟引文係基本<br />\n作文都好好好重要<br />\n利申15年 lv5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇買卷 識得有人15年dse 大卷有39/60 作文得50分左右 就5* 其實係考評局手上拎40/60係咪都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係學校拎開42-44/60左右 好驚到時出去考 個落差會太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61575dfa3b4478dad17df391e59a73307d5b3f2","tid":34480,"uid":47924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"022926d937cba88f183f8555f7d0ab25d3e78263","tid":34480,"uid":4613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>文學要睇翻歷屆幾年 再揀課文黎搵啦<br />\n寫notes背熟引文係基本<br />\n作文都好好好重要<br />\n利申15年 lv5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇買卷 識得有人15年dse 大卷有39/60 作文得50分左右 就5* 其實係考評局手上拎40/60係咪都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係學校拎開42-44/60左右 好驚到時出去考 個落差會太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n作文反而會睇你sba<br />\n我有個fd羅5*買左份卷返黎睇點知原來作文肥左靠sba羅最高分而拉佢分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f773f691b6cd7d75c14890d08716caabeff438cb","tid":34480,"uid":45756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"係學校成績差到俾miss叫我drop科<br />\n裸考拎3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffefacd516fbbe160f7a9ad1e96813216174cdf","tid":34480,"uid":22339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"加油呀！<br />\n<br />\n利申：16年文學5**"},{"pid":"43cbe205f7767e491e8f4f7194f91936bd3ac570","tid":34480,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油呀！<br />\n<br />\n利申：16年文學5**</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩攻略"},{"pid":"6ddf4a1f378af7f32051b55adfc374c30ece3e1e","tid":34480,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油呀！<br />\n<br />\n利申：16年文學5**</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴/絲有冇買卷 個cut off係點？可唔可以分享下<img sr