g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea356ba24985e7c9837c8298df4f63fb5a68069","tid":34480,"uid":22339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加油呀！<br />\n<br />\n利申：16年文學5**</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴/絲有冇買卷 個cut off係點？可唔可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有買到卷 <br />\n<br />\nPaper2 我覺得揀題目好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 温得熟都不及題目問法顯淺重要 我開卷個時考個幾篇都唔係温得最熟個堆 我係答蘇秦同將進酒 呢兩篇本身唔難 題目又唔伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩想知再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73876ec2b22dbdb4d908d6ff2cae74ecefbfe55","tid":34480,"uid":55013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"當年5*<br />\n<br />\n課文果時溫左每課4次 啲大熱課文即係庖丁 西施溫左成6-7 次 由九月開始日日溫1-2課 溫哂再重頭溫過 諗返都幾癲"},{"pid":"0aa54552b75e7225c89730983c20cf445909ec1d","tid":34480,"uid":33807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"個post好似沉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但小弟想知自己應唔應該讀落去..."},{"pid":"fed2d753d05e63b3f2036ef29e7b80f518850da3","tid":34480,"uid":36107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個post好似沉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但小弟想知自己應唔應該讀落去...</blockquote><br />\n唔想讀?"},{"pid":"aa0d6ff0601dcdbeda5eda87a6b9cdd6ad5d68b6","tid":34480,"uid":33807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個post好似沉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但小弟想知自己應唔應該讀落去...</blockquote><br />\n唔想讀?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家讀緊3個x 諗緊drop唔drop 自己冇乜興趣同耐心讀 但學校啲老師都話我讀到...<br />\n<br />\